      <abstract id="aspace_2fc5b718cf56d02e72889e14f6422530">The Marianne L. Garber Collection of
        Shenandoah Valley Documents, 1780-1899, contains one journal written by William Mathias
        Harner from 1847-1861, eight legal and business documents dating from 1815- 1899, and ten
        land deeds and indentures dating from 1780-1887.</abstract>
    </did>
